Mingle Dependency Tracker Release Notes
=======================================

Release Notes for v1.1.1-14
----------------------------

Changes
~~~~~~~
* support for multi-project programs
  - recording of cross-project dependencies
  - program-level reporting
* support for large projects
  - ability to filter the cards displayed
  - performance improvements

Restrictions
~~~~~~~~~~~~
* [Story #675] In program mode, all users of the Dependency Tracker
  must have at least readonly access to all projects in the program.

Release Notes for v1.0.0-244
-----------------------------

Changes
~~~~~~~
* mixed card type dependencies
* redesigned UI
* Mingle 3.2 support
